{"thig5.6:0.1":"Therigatha 5.6 ","thig5.6:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thig5.6:0.3":"Mittakalitherigatha ","thig5.6:1.1":"“Saddhaya pabbajitvana, ","thig5.6:1.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thig5.6:1.3":"Vicarimham tena tena, ","thig5.6:1.4":"labhasakkaraussuka. ","thig5.6:2.1":"Rincitva paramam attham, ","thig5.6:2.2":"hinamattham aseviham; ","thig5.6:2.3":"Kilesanam vasam gantva, ","thig5.6:2.4":"samannattham na bujjhiham. ","thig5.6:3.1":"Tassa me ahu samvego, ","thig5.6:3.2":"nisinnaya viharake; ","thig5.6:3.3":"Ummaggapatipannamhi, ","thig5.6:3.4":"tanhaya vasamagata. ","thig5.6:4.1":"Appakam jivitam mayham, ","thig5.6:4.2":"jara byadhi ca maddati; ","thig5.6:4.3":"Purayam bhijjati kayo, ","thig5.6:4.4":"na me kalo pamajjitum. ","thig5.6:5.1":"Yathabhutamavekkhanti, ","thig5.6:5.2":"khandhanam udayabbayam; ","thig5.6:5.3":"Vimuttacitta utthasim, ","thig5.6:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thig5.6:6.1":"… Mitta kali theri …. "}